- `_shared.tsx`: Replaced `style={{ "--reveal-delay": ... }}` + CSS var class with direct `[transition-delay:${delay}ms]` Tailwind class
- `progress.tsx`: Dropped `--p-offset` custom variable entirely; now uses `--radix-progress-indicator-transform` set automatically by Radix UI, and removed the unused `value` destructuring so it flows through `...props` to Radix
