**File split:**
- `DesignDisplaySections.tsx` reduced from 587 → 362 lines (Interactive + Display + Data sections)
- `DesignLayoutPrimitives.tsx` created (243 lines) holding Layout + Form Controls + Finance + Session sections

`tsc --noEmit` and `eslint --fix` both clean.
